  <p><strong>Unidentified participant:</strong><span class="unclear tooltip" title="Text was unclear">[What do you think of]</span> exaggeration as a literary device?</p>
  <hr/>
  <p><strong>William Faulkner:</strong>I think it's&#x2014;it's valid, just like fantasy, just like
                    comedy, just like tragedy, just like inversion. They are&#x2014;are valid in the sense
