                     <span class="unclear tooltip" title="Text was unclear">[Some authors]</span> keep on doing that.
                </p>
  <hr/>
  <p><strong>William Faulkner:</strong>No, no, it's that character that rings that bell, not me. <span class="event tooltip" title="There was some audience laughter happening">[audience laughter]</span> 
